1
00:00:00,720 --> 00:00:03,520
♪Shrugging off past burdens♪

2
00:00:03,520 --> 00:00:06,110
♪Beneath the mask, who am I?♪

3
00:00:06,780 --> 00:00:10,180
♪Release and find wider shores♪

4
00:00:11,880 --> 00:00:14,890
♪Love's a riddle, and rain pours heavy♪

5
00:00:15,260 --> 00:00:17,790
♪Crossed paths, now downward fall♪

6
00:00:18,130 --> 00:00:21,570
♪From dust arises starlight's spark♪

7
00:00:23,320 --> 00:00:28,540
♪Tearing through
the night's dense blockade♪

8
00:00:29,220 --> 00:00:34,300
♪Heart's flame illuminates all solitude♪

9
00:00:35,100 --> 00:00:37,590
♪Let time's sails drift endlessly♪

10
00:00:37,590 --> 00:00:40,200
♪Through wandering exile♪

11
00:00:40,720 --> 00:00:47,980
♪Breaking free from the cocoon,
I start anew♪

12
00:00:48,950 --> 00:00:51,710
♪Moon as song, life as flame♪

13
00:00:51,770 --> 00:00:54,610
♪Nameless heart clings fiercely♪

14
00:00:54,900 --> 00:00:55,930
♪Let me♪

15
00:00:56,120 --> 00:01:00,200
♪Charge toward the next raging river♪

16
00:01:00,650 --> 00:01:03,330
♪Moon darts, snow falls♪

17
00:01:03,620 --> 00:01:06,320
♪We tread rugged paths to reunite♪

18
00:01:06,490 --> 00:01:07,960
♪Hands held tight♪

19
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:12,130
♪We forever live for love's sake♪

20
00:01:12,490 --> 00:01:22,740
♪Shadow's spear burns fiercely♪

21
00:01:24,170 --> 00:01:29,720
=Legend of The Female General=

22
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:32,800
=Episode 20=

23
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,160
Storm the city!

24
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:57,440
Attack!

25
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,360
Sweetie.

26
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:51,720
This pot looks pretty heavy.

27
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:54,280
If the Wutuo forces really break in,

28
00:02:54,530 --> 00:02:55,440
can you even swing it?

29
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:57,600
No, I can't.

30
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:58,440
But I'll throw it

31
00:02:58,480 --> 00:02:59,440
at them.

32
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,680
Killing one enemy is good.

33
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:02,720
Killing two

34
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,000
is better.

35
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:09,360
With enemies coming,

36
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:10,840
we must stand united.

37
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:12,080
Jiyang is my home.

38
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,680
If home is gone,

39
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,840
what's the point of living?

40
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,160
Exactly.

41
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:19,010
My brother and father are
on the battlefield.

42
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:21,000
I want to cheer them in victory.

43
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:22,440
You're right.

44
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:23,720
Women

45
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:25,280
should also be tough.

46
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:27,360
If officials' families only

47
00:03:27,440 --> 00:03:28,440
want self-preservation,

48
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:30,360
how can we expect soldiers

49
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:31,600
to fight on the front lines?

50
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:34,000
Let's fight enemies!

51
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:36,480
- Sure!
- Let's fight them!

52
00:04:38,710 --> 00:04:41,020
(Compassionate Salvation)

53
00:04:41,060 --> 00:04:43,220
(Radiant Illumination)

54
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:01,840
Who are you?

55
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:08,360
That's not important. Attack!

56
00:05:44,320 --> 00:05:45,400
Charge!

57
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,320
(Three Passes)
Fire arrows!

58
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,520
Feinu.

59
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,570
You lead the vanguard out of the city.

60
00:05:53,840 --> 00:05:55,040
Muyi will lead Jiyang troops

61
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:55,960
to guard the gate.

62
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,840
Not a single Wutuo man

63
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:00,000
shall enter Jiyang!

64
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,560
- Understood!
- Understood!

65
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,560
Once the gate opens,

66
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:12,040
lead the main force
against the Wutuo army first.

67
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:14,360
Then I'll take an elite squad

68
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:17,280
to divert Huyate
and his heavy armor troops,

69
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,970
luring them away
from the main battlefield.

70
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,560
The remaining Wutuo forces

71
00:06:22,320 --> 00:06:23,400
will be leaderless.

72
00:06:26,280 --> 00:06:27,120
Commander.

73
00:06:27,600 --> 00:06:28,720
Let me lead the elite squad

74
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:31,000
to lure away Huyate and his heavy armor.

75
00:06:32,040 --> 00:06:32,880
No.

76
00:06:33,159 --> 00:06:34,200
To divert Huyate,

77
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:35,840
we need someone of high standing.

78
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:37,600
The Wutuo loathe me.

79
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,440
Therefore,

80
00:06:40,320 --> 00:06:41,520
I'm the right one.

81
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,159
Actually, in Jiyang, there is someone

82
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,280
of higher standing

83
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:47,680
than you.

84
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:54,040
Quick!

85
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:15,520
You want to impersonate Princess Mengji?

86
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:17,000
Yes.

87
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,280
Do you understand the risks?

88
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:33,159
I do,

89
00:07:34,080 --> 00:07:35,440
so I can't let you go.

90
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,720
As our commander-in-chief,

91
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:41,120
the entire army's fate relies on you.

92
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,200
You can't take unnecessary risks.

93
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:49,760
I know you are

94
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,760
worried about my safety.

95
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:54,120
But you must realize

96
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,320
that once I wear this armor,

97
00:07:57,159 --> 00:07:58,360
I become a soldier,

98
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,320
fearless of death.

99
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:06,920
Medic!

100
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:08,680
Come quickly!

101
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:09,520
There's another one!

102
00:08:09,520 --> 00:08:10,360
Hurry!

103
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:12,600
Move faster!

104
00:08:12,840 --> 00:08:13,800
He Yan, receive orders!

105
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,120
Come back alive.

106
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:20,920
Yes!

107
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,520
Quickly!

108
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:37,840
Medic!

109
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:39,840
Medic!

110
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:41,360
Hurry!

111
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:42,919
He's dying!

112
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:43,760
Let me check.

113
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:53,960
Faster!

114
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,080
This will hurt.

115
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,040
Bear with it.

116
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:09,600
Alright.

117
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,680
Prepare the horses!

118
00:09:54,680 --> 00:09:55,520
Yes!

119
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:02,520
Charge!

120
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:06,240
- Attack!
- Attack!

121
00:10:36,740 --> 00:10:38,000
Whoever captures Xiao Jue alive

122
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:40,840
will be handsomely rewarded.

123
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:42,280
- Attack!
- Attack!

124
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:51,320
Attack!

125
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:34,040
Mu Hongjin is trying to escape.

126
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:36,200
Heavy infantry! Capture her alive!

127
00:11:57,160 --> 00:11:58,000
(He Yan.)

128
00:11:58,560 --> 00:11:59,920
(You must return safely.)

129
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,280
Seize Mu Hongjin!

130
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,400
Don't let her escape!

131
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:36,080
(Wutuo forces)

132
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:37,440
(are accustomed to land battles.)

133
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:39,280
(Horses aren't water-adept.)

134
00:12:39,280 --> 00:12:40,800
There's a riverbank east of the city.

135
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,280
It's a risky move.

136
00:12:42,560 --> 00:12:43,560
Destroy the leader first.

137
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:45,040
Capture Huyate,

138
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:46,920
and the battle can turn around.

139
00:13:13,920 --> 00:13:15,240
You're not Mu Hongjin.

140
00:13:15,640 --> 00:13:17,000
Trash like you

141
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,760
isn't worth Her Highness' effort.

142
00:13:19,560 --> 00:13:21,080
You're courting death.

143
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:57,600
You're seeking death!

144
00:13:57,840 --> 00:14:00,360
I'm killing you at any cost.

145
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:16,680
(Chai Anxi?)

146
00:14:38,760 --> 00:14:39,760
I just spotted Chai Anxi.

147
00:14:39,880 --> 00:14:40,720
But he vanished.

148
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,300
You must find him.

149
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:43,600
Yes.

150
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:35,040
(Dear sister,)

151
00:15:36,080 --> 00:15:38,480
(I gave you mercy.)

152
00:15:39,280 --> 00:15:40,720
(Yet you rejected it.)

153
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:42,640
(You let me down.)

154
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:43,870
(Bring honor to our family?)

155
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:45,240
(You don't deserve to do that.)

156
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:47,200
(My family needs only one heir.)

157
00:15:47,280 --> 00:15:48,360
(Prepare to die!)

158
00:15:48,880 --> 00:15:50,080
(Prepare to die!)

159
00:15:51,080 --> 00:15:53,080
(Our family doesn't need you.)

160
00:15:53,160 --> 00:15:54,200
(Your death)

161
00:15:54,720 --> 00:15:56,680
(will ensure our family's peace.)

162
00:16:59,680 --> 00:17:00,520
Commander.

163
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:03,240
Commander, have we won?

164
00:17:06,440 --> 00:17:07,280
Listen.

165
00:17:08,000 --> 00:17:09,000
We've won.

166
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:12,640
- We've won!
- We've won!

167
00:17:18,760 --> 00:17:19,599
Great!

168
00:17:20,280 --> 00:17:21,160
We've won.

169
00:17:25,560 --> 00:17:26,400
Indeed.

170
00:17:28,119 --> 00:17:28,960
We've won.

171
00:17:30,600 --> 00:17:31,440
- We won!
- We won!

172
00:17:31,520 --> 00:17:32,680
- We won!
- We won!

173
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:33,720
- We won!
- We won!

174
00:17:34,840 --> 00:17:35,680
- We won!
- We won!

175
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:42,760
- We won!
- We won!

176
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:44,440
We won!

177
00:17:49,880 --> 00:17:50,800
Splendid!

178
00:17:52,040 --> 00:17:52,880
- We won!
- We won!

179
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:56,640
- We won!
- We won!

180
00:17:58,160 --> 00:17:59,000
We won!

181
00:17:59,000 --> 00:17:59,840
We won!

182
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:01,760
- We won!
- We won!

183
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:03,840
We won!

184
00:18:05,160 --> 00:18:06,000
We won!

185
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:07,240
Brilliant!

186
00:18:07,560 --> 00:18:08,440
- We won!
- We won!

187
00:18:11,200 --> 00:18:12,040
We've won!

188
00:18:13,720 --> 00:18:14,560
We've won!

189
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:16,280
Your Highness.

190
00:18:16,960 --> 00:18:17,800
We've won.

191
00:18:58,260 --> 00:18:59,780
♪I've seen the mountains♪

192
00:18:59,780 --> 00:19:01,330
♪And trodden through ice♪

193
00:19:01,330 --> 00:19:03,780
♪Day after day, I venture alone♪

194
00:19:04,310 --> 00:19:05,890
♪Destiny is my creed♪

195
00:19:05,890 --> 00:19:07,450
♪Ideals surge beneath the surface♪

196
00:19:07,450 --> 00:19:09,780
♪Igniting the flame against the winds♪

197
00:19:10,550 --> 00:19:12,010
♪A restless yearning in my soul♪

198
00:19:12,010 --> 00:19:13,570
♪Gazing through the mire♪

199
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:15,760
What's on your mind?

200
00:19:16,210 --> 00:19:18,060
♪Charge ahead with blazing fervor♪

201
00:19:19,720 --> 00:19:20,560
Nothing.

202
00:19:22,520 --> 00:19:24,720
Let's report to Her Highness.

203
00:19:26,290 --> 00:19:28,800
♪There must always be a longing♪

204
00:19:29,360 --> 00:19:33,880
♪Disregard the wounds to seek the light♪

205
00:19:33,880 --> 00:19:34,720
Hold my hand.

206
00:19:34,720 --> 00:19:36,880
♪Light shines upon my heart♪

207
00:19:36,980 --> 00:19:40,900
♪Unveiling scars,
I choose to swim upstream♪

208
00:19:40,900 --> 00:19:43,020
♪The resonance of courage
rings loud and clear♪

209
00:19:43,020 --> 00:19:47,040
♪It's the boldness
that defines existence♪

210
00:19:47,040 --> 00:19:48,980
♪Chasing the light within my heart♪

211
00:19:49,160 --> 00:19:52,990
♪Burying frailty,
embracing life through death♪

212
00:19:53,240 --> 00:19:59,000
♪You'll meet gazes where storms brew♪

213
00:19:59,880 --> 00:20:03,960
♪With our unwavering true love,
brave the world with me♪

214
00:20:03,960 --> 00:20:04,920
You've all worked hard.

215
00:20:05,280 --> 00:20:06,880
On behalf of Jiyang's people,

216
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:08,520
I thank you all.

217
00:20:09,480 --> 00:20:10,320
My pleasure.

218
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:11,520
Protecting the nation

219
00:20:11,840 --> 00:20:12,680
and people

220
00:20:13,160 --> 00:20:14,480
is our duty.

221
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:15,840
That's an honor.

222
00:20:16,520 --> 00:20:17,920
Congratulations, General Fengyun.

223
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:20,640
I'm glad you're safe.

224
00:20:21,520 --> 00:20:22,600
I appreciate your concern.

225
00:20:25,120 --> 00:20:25,960
Your Highness.

226
00:20:26,520 --> 00:20:29,040
I found Mr. Liu's body near the mansion.

227
00:20:29,600 --> 00:20:32,080
There were many Wutuo men's bodies
surrounding him.

228
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:34,360
Their weapons were poisonous.

229
00:20:35,120 --> 00:20:36,280
Mr. Liu was fatally poisoned.

230
00:20:36,280 --> 00:20:37,310
Enemies outnumbered him.

231
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:38,800
He died of exhaustion.

232
00:20:46,040 --> 00:20:47,080
My master?

233
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:49,760
That's not true.

234
00:20:53,200 --> 00:20:54,280
My master couldn't have...

235
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:41,440
(This pair of bracelets
is called Joyful Hearts.)

236
00:21:42,240 --> 00:21:44,670
Lovers wearing them

237
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:46,440
will never be parted.

238
00:21:48,520 --> 00:21:50,040
Is this your beloved?

239
00:21:52,560 --> 00:21:54,000
(Buy a pair for the lady.)

240
00:21:54,440 --> 00:21:56,800
You two will be together forever.

241
00:21:57,680 --> 00:21:58,680
Did you hear that?

242
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:00,350
Aren't you buying me this?

243
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:04,120
She's not my beloved.

244
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:22,280
Liar.

245
00:22:23,920 --> 00:22:24,840
You liar.

246
00:22:32,960 --> 00:22:33,800
What's wrong?

247
00:22:34,640 --> 00:22:35,480
Are you upset?

248
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:36,770
None of your business.

249
00:22:38,080 --> 00:22:39,360
Did I upset you?

250
00:22:43,080 --> 00:22:43,920
Liu Buwang.

251
00:22:43,920 --> 00:22:45,380
Why didn't you buy me the bracelets?

252
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:47,320
If it were anything else,

253
00:22:47,520 --> 00:22:48,640
I'd promise you.

254
00:22:49,040 --> 00:22:49,880
Really?

255
00:22:50,280 --> 00:22:51,440
Don't trick me again.

256
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:53,440
I mean it.

257
00:22:56,160 --> 00:22:57,000
Well,

258
00:22:57,520 --> 00:22:58,920
go outside the city with me?

259
00:23:00,760 --> 00:23:01,920
I'll share a secret.

260
00:23:02,360 --> 00:23:03,200
In a temple

261
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:05,090
lies a passage leading out of the city.

262
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:07,240
A passage?

263
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:08,800
You already promised me.

264
00:23:08,800 --> 00:23:09,640
Keep your word.

265
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:10,560
Let's go.

266
00:23:13,950 --> 00:23:14,920
(Radiant Illumination)
Here we are.

267
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:16,900
Alright.

268
00:23:22,430 --> 00:23:25,440
♪Through endless nights, I walk alone♪

269
00:23:25,440 --> 00:23:28,740
♪Heartache swirls like ceaseless winds♪

270
00:23:33,220 --> 00:23:36,350
♪Yet I yearn to stand opposed to you♪

271
00:23:36,350 --> 00:23:39,950
♪Seeking fleeting clarity♪

272
00:23:40,420 --> 00:23:44,210
♪Imprisoned within memories♪

273
00:23:44,640 --> 00:23:47,270
♪Upon towering fortress walls♪

274
00:23:47,270 --> 00:23:50,050
♪Brooding over lamented pasts♪

275
00:23:50,050 --> 00:23:52,910
♪Where shall light be found♪

276
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:55,170
♪Once♪

277
00:23:55,600 --> 00:23:57,970
♪I had an unbreakable faith♪

278
00:23:59,080 --> 00:24:00,040
Jiyang

279
00:24:01,240 --> 00:24:02,080
is safe now.

280
00:24:02,600 --> 00:24:03,680
That's good.

281
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:06,320
♪I'm shrouded in darkness♪

282
00:24:06,590 --> 00:24:09,720
♪Resent old dreams like drifting clouds♪

283
00:24:10,210 --> 00:24:11,680
♪Heartache♪

284
00:24:11,890 --> 00:24:15,170
♪Resenting the lonely years♪

285
00:24:15,600 --> 00:24:17,340
♪Why♪

286
00:24:17,340 --> 00:24:19,070
♪Not let it go♪

287
00:24:20,080 --> 00:24:24,490
♪Tears crystallize to frost♪

288
00:24:25,560 --> 00:24:28,190
♪Clutching stubborn obsessions♪

289
00:24:28,460 --> 00:24:31,590
♪Yet falling into folly♪

290
00:24:31,870 --> 00:24:33,700
♪Fading into oblivion♪

291
00:24:33,700 --> 00:24:36,830
♪Yet memories surge everywhere♪

292
00:24:37,810 --> 00:24:40,540
♪After the separation♪

293
00:24:40,540 --> 00:24:46,290
♪Who will be with you♪

294
00:24:53,600 --> 00:24:54,640
Hongjin.

295
00:25:09,170 --> 00:25:11,620
♪You are my light♪

296
00:25:11,760 --> 00:25:12,720
Hongjin.

297
00:25:13,800 --> 00:25:15,480
I wish you peace.

298
00:25:15,570 --> 00:25:17,210
♪Get lost♪

299
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:19,960
Live

300
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:24,640
well.

301
00:25:25,330 --> 00:25:29,640
♪Mournful through night skies♪

302
00:25:30,900 --> 00:25:33,670
♪How dare I hope♪

303
00:25:33,670 --> 00:25:37,380
♪That twilight outshines vastness♪

304
00:25:37,380 --> 00:25:39,070
♪Ultimately♪

305
00:25:39,070 --> 00:25:42,850
♪Await ancients
to bid farewell to the past♪

306
00:25:43,250 --> 00:25:46,020
♪After parting♪

307
00:25:46,020 --> 00:25:52,490
♪My heart feels adrift♪

308
00:27:02,480 --> 00:27:03,960
Maybe I should go check on them.

309
00:27:04,440 --> 00:27:05,280
No.

310
00:27:05,360 --> 00:27:06,480
This is not something

311
00:27:06,840 --> 00:27:08,280
you and I can fix.

312
00:27:09,840 --> 00:27:11,560
Leave them alone for a moment.

313
00:27:33,800 --> 00:27:34,640
Commander.

314
00:27:34,760 --> 00:27:36,000
Thanks for guarding the door.

315
00:27:39,400 --> 00:27:40,480
Why are you staring at me?

316
00:27:41,320 --> 00:27:42,800
Is there something on my face?

317
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:49,720
Ugly.

318
00:27:51,440 --> 00:27:52,280
What?

319
00:27:52,840 --> 00:27:53,960
It makes you ugly

320
00:27:55,080 --> 00:27:55,920
when you lie.

321
00:28:02,800 --> 00:28:03,640
I've told you.

322
00:28:04,960 --> 00:28:05,920
Just cry or laugh

323
00:28:06,760 --> 00:28:07,600
if you want to.

324
00:28:08,480 --> 00:28:09,520
Just be yourself.

325
00:28:10,960 --> 00:28:12,200
You don't have to act.

326
00:28:15,080 --> 00:28:15,920
It looks unnatural.

327
00:28:17,760 --> 00:28:18,720
I'm not acting.

328
00:28:20,240 --> 00:28:21,080
It's just

329
00:28:22,560 --> 00:28:23,600
that I can't help.

330
00:28:26,280 --> 00:28:27,200
What do you mean?

331
00:28:29,720 --> 00:28:30,560
Commander.

332
00:28:31,480 --> 00:28:33,000
In this world, only a few people

333
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:34,920
who treated me well.

334
00:28:36,800 --> 00:28:38,240
Less than five people.

335
00:28:48,600 --> 00:28:49,880
Now, one of them is gone.

336
00:29:13,560 --> 00:29:19,710
(Tomb of Hermit Yunlin Liu Buwang)

337
00:29:35,280 --> 00:29:36,120
Yan.

338
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:38,360
I'm sorry for your loss.

339
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:40,280
Miss He.

340
00:29:40,720 --> 00:29:41,560
I'm so sorry.

341
00:29:42,600 --> 00:29:43,440
Miss He.

342
00:29:44,320 --> 00:29:45,440
We're all mere mortals.

343
00:29:46,600 --> 00:29:48,120
Who can truly remain detached?

344
00:29:49,280 --> 00:29:51,000
If we don't force ourselves
to let it go,

345
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:52,520
what else can we do?

346
00:29:56,720 --> 00:29:57,680
Mr. Liu was

347
00:29:58,520 --> 00:29:59,440
free and unrestrained.

348
00:30:01,040 --> 00:30:02,360
If he saw you grieving like this,

349
00:30:03,040 --> 00:30:04,200
he would worry about you.

350
00:30:05,480 --> 00:30:06,320
The living

351
00:30:07,080 --> 00:30:08,280
must move on.

352
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:11,120
They say

353
00:30:12,400 --> 00:30:13,320
that the deceased

354
00:30:14,320 --> 00:30:15,840
would cross the River of Forgetfulness

355
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:17,790
to reach the other shore.

356
00:30:20,480 --> 00:30:21,400
But what's it like

357
00:30:24,000 --> 00:30:25,120
across the river?

358
00:30:52,600 --> 00:30:53,440
Master.

359
00:30:54,880 --> 00:30:56,320
According to Jiyang's customs,

360
00:30:57,040 --> 00:30:57,880
tonight,

361
00:30:58,360 --> 00:30:59,680
the family should prepare food

362
00:31:00,520 --> 00:31:01,560
to send off the departed.

363
00:31:03,360 --> 00:31:04,200
I have

364
00:31:04,520 --> 00:31:06,680
prepared your favorite dishes.

365
00:31:07,440 --> 00:31:08,280
Jiyang

366
00:31:08,560 --> 00:31:10,120
is now recovering steadily.

367
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:11,720
All is well.

368
00:31:12,480 --> 00:31:13,320
And everyone is safe.

369
00:31:15,360 --> 00:31:16,280
Master.

370
00:31:17,760 --> 00:31:19,000
May you rest in peace.

371
00:31:22,160 --> 00:31:23,000
Let me

372
00:31:23,760 --> 00:31:24,600
toast you.

373
00:31:47,360 --> 00:31:48,200
Your Highness.

374
00:31:49,000 --> 00:31:51,200
I brought some dishes for your master.

375
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:05,320
After all these years,

376
00:32:06,440 --> 00:32:08,600
your master's taste in food
remains unchanged.

377
00:32:13,520 --> 00:32:14,480
Sweet and sour fish.

378
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:16,080
You didn't put any sugar

379
00:32:16,480 --> 00:32:17,920
in this dish?

380
00:32:18,640 --> 00:32:19,600
My master

381
00:32:20,200 --> 00:32:23,000
loved sugarless sweet and sour fish.

382
00:32:23,800 --> 00:32:26,040
He never put sugar in it.

383
00:32:26,520 --> 00:32:27,760
I used to tease him

384
00:32:28,440 --> 00:32:30,680
that it was sweet and sour fish
without sugar,

385
00:32:31,040 --> 00:32:33,160
and he could eat sour fish.

386
00:32:34,280 --> 00:32:35,200
Only later did I know

387
00:32:36,040 --> 00:32:37,200
it was because the one

388
00:32:37,800 --> 00:32:39,480
my master had been missing

389
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:41,760
liked

390
00:32:42,280 --> 00:32:43,800
to eat sugarless sweet and sour fish.

391
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:48,320
I always knew

392
00:32:49,240 --> 00:32:50,360
he liked me.

393
00:32:52,720 --> 00:32:53,800
I refused to meet him

394
00:32:54,640 --> 00:32:55,880
because he broke his promise.

395
00:33:01,480 --> 00:33:02,400
But the bracelet

396
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:03,240
made me realize

397
00:33:03,520 --> 00:33:04,920
he must have had his reasons.

398
00:33:05,520 --> 00:33:06,560
Thinking about it now,

399
00:33:07,040 --> 00:33:08,520
what difference would it make?

400
00:33:09,160 --> 00:33:12,120
I'm Mu Hongjin of the Mengji Mansion.

401
00:33:12,640 --> 00:33:14,160
I'm Mu Hongjin of Jiyang.

402
00:33:14,800 --> 00:33:15,640
I could never

403
00:33:16,600 --> 00:33:18,120
be his Mu Hongjin.

404
00:33:22,080 --> 00:33:22,920
He Yan.

405
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:25,080
Fate didn't bind me to your master,

406
00:33:25,640 --> 00:33:26,560
but I've genuinely

407
00:33:26,800 --> 00:33:28,320
come to regard you as family.

408
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:30,640
My greatest regret

409
00:33:30,960 --> 00:33:32,080
is that I didn't go out

410
00:33:33,240 --> 00:33:34,720
to meet him that night.

411
00:33:36,360 --> 00:33:38,240
Even just a glimpse from afar

412
00:33:39,120 --> 00:33:39,960
would be better.

413
00:33:46,880 --> 00:33:48,640
Cherish the one you like.

414
00:33:49,720 --> 00:33:50,720
Don't repeat the mistake

415
00:33:51,360 --> 00:33:52,880
your master and I made.

416
00:33:54,720 --> 00:33:55,640
It's lucky

417
00:33:56,240 --> 00:33:57,720
to meet the one you love

418
00:33:57,800 --> 00:33:59,400
in your life.

419
00:34:00,360 --> 00:34:01,520
Once you find the right one,

420
00:34:02,000 --> 00:34:03,640
don't let him go.

421
00:34:04,480 --> 00:34:05,600
Give him a chance

422
00:34:06,080 --> 00:34:06,920
and trust him.

423
00:34:07,680 --> 00:34:09,040
It also means a chance for you.

424
00:34:14,840 --> 00:34:15,840
I see, Your Highness.

425
00:34:37,960 --> 00:34:38,800
Commander.

426
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:39,840
Why are you here?

427
00:34:40,520 --> 00:34:41,360
Once you returned,

428
00:34:41,560 --> 00:34:42,760
you went to restaurants,

429
00:34:43,239 --> 00:34:44,480
preparing food for Mr. Liu.

430
00:34:45,440 --> 00:34:46,440
But you eat nothing.

431
00:35:03,160 --> 00:35:04,000
Let's eat together.

432
00:35:34,720 --> 00:35:35,560
Sir.

433
00:35:35,560 --> 00:35:37,160
Xiao Jue has taken Chai Anxi back.

434
00:35:37,160 --> 00:35:38,480
Chai Anxi is now unconscious.

435
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:40,120
He's now at the Cui Mansion.

436
00:35:40,400 --> 00:35:41,520
Cheng Lisu and Song Taotao

437
00:35:41,520 --> 00:35:42,360
are treating him.

438
00:35:42,480 --> 00:35:43,680
Chancellor Xu sent a letter,

439
00:35:43,680 --> 00:35:45,060
urging you to act quickly.

440
00:35:45,060 --> 00:35:46,840
Should I go kill Chai Anxi now?

441
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:47,800
I suspect

442
00:35:48,160 --> 00:35:49,720
Chai Anxi holds crucial information.

443
00:35:50,240 --> 00:35:51,920
So, I need to verify details with him.

444
00:35:52,920 --> 00:35:54,320
Have you noticed something?

445
00:35:54,360 --> 00:35:55,200
Chai Anxi

446
00:35:55,200 --> 00:35:56,640
was Xiao Zhongwu's deputy general.

447
00:35:56,960 --> 00:35:58,760
He faked his death
after the Mingshui Battle.

448
00:35:58,760 --> 00:36:01,080
Xiao Jue's search for him
is understandable.

449
00:36:02,080 --> 00:36:03,320
But to kill him,

450
00:36:03,720 --> 00:36:04,680
Chancellor Xu sent me

451
00:36:05,440 --> 00:36:06,520
and even contacted Wutuo.

452
00:36:07,400 --> 00:36:08,440
It makes me realize

453
00:36:08,760 --> 00:36:09,960
that he and Chai Anxi must

454
00:36:10,200 --> 00:36:11,040
share a dark history.

455
00:36:11,520 --> 00:36:12,440
Are you suspecting

456
00:36:12,700 --> 00:36:15,000
Chancellor Xu is related
to the Mingshui Battle's defeat?

457
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,520
We'll know the answer

458
00:36:17,080 --> 00:36:18,400
when Chai Anxi wakes.

459
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,840
Chai Anxi knows you.

460
00:36:21,600 --> 00:36:22,440
If he wakes,

461
00:36:22,560 --> 00:36:24,040
will he implicate you?

462
00:36:24,240 --> 00:36:25,080
No.

463
00:36:25,600 --> 00:36:27,000
Chai Anxi values loyalty.

464
00:36:27,080 --> 00:36:27,920
He'd never

465
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:29,800
betray his lifesaver.

466
00:36:30,320 --> 00:36:31,160
Moreover,

467
00:36:32,120 --> 00:36:33,200
even if he says something,

468
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:35,320
I have contingency plans.

469
00:36:36,640 --> 00:36:38,400
Now that Chai Anxi's at the Cui Mansion,

470
00:36:38,920 --> 00:36:40,320
as an Inspector,

471
00:36:40,760 --> 00:36:41,680
I should pay a visit.

472
00:37:08,240 --> 00:37:09,800
Though Chai Anxi's life is stabilized,

473
00:37:09,960 --> 00:37:10,920
his injuries are severe.

474
00:37:11,520 --> 00:37:12,930
Song Taotao is preparing medicine.

475
00:37:13,200 --> 00:37:14,040
I'll leave it to you.

476
00:37:16,960 --> 00:37:17,800
Chu Zhao?

477
00:37:18,840 --> 00:37:19,680
What brings you here?

478
00:37:29,840 --> 00:37:30,680
Commander Xiao.

479
00:37:34,240 --> 00:37:35,520
I heard General Fengyun

480
00:37:35,760 --> 00:37:36,680
found a soldier

481
00:37:37,160 --> 00:37:38,120
who supposedly died

482
00:37:38,160 --> 00:37:39,120
at the Mingshui Battle.

483
00:37:39,640 --> 00:37:41,000
I wonder why a dead man

484
00:37:41,240 --> 00:37:42,320
came back to life.

485
00:37:42,800 --> 00:37:44,160
It's pretty strange.

486
00:37:44,520 --> 00:37:45,920
As an Inspector,

487
00:37:46,320 --> 00:37:47,320
I must figure this out.

488
00:37:48,040 --> 00:37:48,880
It made sense.

489
00:37:49,880 --> 00:37:50,960
I just found this man

490
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:52,600
and wanted to inform you.

491
00:37:52,960 --> 00:37:53,800
But unexpectedly,

492
00:37:54,080 --> 00:37:54,920
you came.

493
00:37:56,160 --> 00:37:57,320
You are

494
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:58,920
so well-informed.

495
00:38:01,080 --> 00:38:02,000
I have to be alert

496
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:03,760
as His Majesty's courtier.

497
00:38:05,680 --> 00:38:06,760
He remains unconscious,

498
00:38:07,120 --> 00:38:08,160
so we can't question him.

499
00:38:08,160 --> 00:38:09,000
However,

500
00:38:09,000 --> 00:38:10,080
Cheng Lisu and Song Taotao

501
00:38:10,360 --> 00:38:11,640
are trying to treat him.

502
00:38:12,040 --> 00:38:12,880
When he wakes,

503
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:14,680
you'll be informed.

504
00:38:15,200 --> 00:38:16,640
Thanks, Commander Xiao.

505
00:38:17,200 --> 00:38:18,520
I'll take my leave.

506
00:38:20,520 --> 00:38:21,360
See you.

507
00:38:22,520 --> 00:38:23,360
See you.

508
00:38:29,800 --> 00:38:30,640
Commander.

509
00:38:30,760 --> 00:38:32,160
Why share details with him?

510
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:33,920
He's Xu Jingfu's disciple.

511
00:38:34,520 --> 00:38:35,640
He's up to no good.

512
00:38:36,800 --> 00:38:38,080
His official position

513
00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:39,680
grants him authority.

514
00:38:40,760 --> 00:38:42,440
Avoidance won't work.

515
00:38:44,720 --> 00:38:45,560
Post more guards

516
00:38:46,000 --> 00:38:46,840
around the courtyard.

517
00:38:47,600 --> 00:38:48,600
Prevent the opponents

518
00:38:49,200 --> 00:38:50,040
from breaking in.

519
00:38:50,920 --> 00:38:51,760
Yes.

520
00:38:56,070 --> 00:38:58,230
♪Light shines upon my heart♪

521
00:38:58,330 --> 00:39:02,250
♪Unveiling scars,
I choose to swim upstream♪

522
00:39:02,430 --> 00:39:04,370
♪The resonance of courage
rings loud and clear♪

523
00:39:04,470 --> 00:39:09,400
♪It's the boldness
that defines existence♪

524
00:39:21,490 --> 00:39:22,900
♪I've seen the mountains♪

525
00:39:23,100 --> 00:39:24,510
♪And trodden through ice♪

526
00:39:24,780 --> 00:39:27,600
♪Day after day, I venture alone♪

527
00:39:27,900 --> 00:39:29,290
♪Destiny is my creed♪

528
00:39:29,350 --> 00:39:30,750
♪Ideals surge beneath the surface♪

529
00:39:30,900 --> 00:39:32,700
♪Igniting the flame against the winds♪

530
00:39:33,900 --> 00:39:35,370
♪A restless yearning in my soul♪

531
00:39:35,540 --> 00:39:36,820
♪Gazing through the mire♪

532
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:39,390
♪Who cares about this boundless void♪

533
00:39:39,590 --> 00:39:41,640
♪Charge ahead with blazing fervor♪

534
00:39:42,780 --> 00:39:44,610
♪Stubbornly fighting with my life♪

535
00:39:46,570 --> 00:39:49,480
♪Soaring across the world's expanse♪

536
00:39:49,570 --> 00:39:52,240
♪There must always be a longing♪

537
00:39:52,690 --> 00:39:57,750
♪Disregard the wounds to seek the light♪

538
00:39:58,090 --> 00:40:00,090
♪Light shines upon my heart♪

539
00:40:00,410 --> 00:40:04,050
♪Unveiling scars,
I choose to swim upstream♪

540
00:40:04,290 --> 00:40:06,180
♪The resonance of courage
rings loud and clear♪

541
00:40:06,210 --> 00:40:10,060
♪It's the boldness
that defines existence♪

542
00:40:10,410 --> 00:40:12,350
♪Chasing the light within my heart♪

543
00:40:12,540 --> 00:40:16,360
♪Burying frailty,
embracing life through death♪

544
00:40:16,620 --> 00:40:22,370
♪You'll meet gazes where storms brew♪

545
00:40:23,260 --> 00:40:28,720
♪With our unwavering true love,
brave the world with me♪

546
00:40:35,880 --> 00:40:38,800
♪Soaring across the world's expanse♪

547
00:40:38,890 --> 00:40:41,550
♪There must always be a longing♪

548
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:47,070
♪Disregard the wounds to seek the light♪

549
00:40:47,400 --> 00:40:49,410
♪Light shines upon my heart♪

550
00:40:49,720 --> 00:40:53,370
♪Unveiling scars,
I choose to swim upstream♪

551
00:40:53,600 --> 00:40:55,500
♪The resonance of courage
rings loud and clear♪

552
00:40:55,530 --> 00:40:59,370
♪It's the boldness
that defines existence♪

553
00:40:59,730 --> 00:41:01,670
♪Chasing the light within my heart♪

554
00:41:01,850 --> 00:41:05,670
♪Burying frailty,
embracing life through death♪

555
00:41:05,930 --> 00:41:11,680
♪You'll meet gazes where storms brew♪

556
00:41:12,570 --> 00:41:18,040
♪With our unwavering true love,
brave the world with me♪
